OL,3,CCouncil approves planning permission
OL,4,Cfor huge gig series in Cardiff park
OL,6,FCardiff Council has approved planning
OL,7,Fpermission for the return of Blackweir
OL,8,FLive gig series, despite opposition.
OL,10,FLast year's series was hailed as a
OL,11,Fmajor success for the city and
OL,12,Fattracted big names such as Alanis
OL,13,FMorissette and Stevie Wonder.
OL,15,FHowever the series also attracted
OL,16,Fcontroversy from groups who frequently
OL,17,Fuse the Bute park on the grounds of
OL,18,Fnoise, environmental impact and more.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
