OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1780589464
OL,3,CCouncil approves planning permission
OL,4,Cfor huge gig series in Cardiff park
OL,6,FDespite this, permission was granted
OL,7,Fto hold the event each summer up to
OL,8,FAugust 2031.
OL,10,FAhead of the approval of the
OL,11,Fapplication, groups opposed to the
OL,12,Fconcert series unsuccessfully
OL,13,Fattempting to get a Welsh Government
OL,14,Fcall-in.
OL,16,FA Welsh Government call-in is a
OL,17,Freserve power where Welsh Ministers
OL,18,Ftake over a planning application
OL,19,Fsubmitted to a local authority and
OL,20,Fdecide the outcome themselves.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
