PN,46203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1780589464
OL,3,CCouncil approves planning permission
OL,4,Cfor huge gig series in Cardiff park
OL,6,FDuring the meeting, Lyn Eynon of the
OL,7,FCardiff Civic Society made a
OL,8,Frepresentation against the gig series.
OL,10,FHe said: "Bute Park was gifted for
OL,11,Fpublic enjoyment, not private events"
OL,12,Fand raised concerns about the impact
OL,13,Fof the summer event on the park's
OL,14,Fnatural environment and the cumulative
OL,15,Feffects of holding it summer after
OL,16,Fsummer.
OL,26,@rD@JOUsD@eO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
