FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1780589464
OL,3,CCouncil approves planning permission
OL,4,Cfor huge gig series in Cardiff park
OL,6,FMr Eynon urged the council to look for
OL,7,F"alternative locations to Blackweir
OL,8,FFields" and criticised the council for
OL,9,Fallowing ticket sales before
OL,10,Fpermission was granted, calling it "no
OL,11,Fway to conduct business."
OL,13,FThe agent speaking on behalf of the
OL,14,Fcouncil said the mitigation strategies
OL,15,Fhad been put in place to address
OL,16,Fconcerns collected during the public
OL,17,Fconsultation and that "Cardiff has a
OL,18,Flong history of hosting major music
OL,19,Fevents" and that Blackweir Live would
OL,20,F"help and promote Cardiff's role as a
OL,21,Fcultural centre".
