PN,46205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1780589464
OL,3,CCouncil approves planning permission
OL,4,Cfor huge gig series in Cardiff park
OL,6,FDuring the debate, some councillors
OL,7,Fraised concerns over the length of
OL,8,Ftime permission was granted for and
OL,9,Fthe noise generated by the
OL,10,Fperformances.
OL,12,FCllr Jon Shimmin said, last year, he
OL,13,Fcould hear the noise from his home in
OL,14,FPenylan and his children (were
OL,15,Fcomplaining about not being able to
OL,16,Fsleep) because of the noise."
OL,26,@vD@ZpmxD@FpnxD@]O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/6
