FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1780589464
OL,3,CCouncil approves planning permission
OL,4,Cfor huge gig series in Cardiff park
OL,6,FAt multiple points during the debate,
OL,7,Fplanning officers repeated that
OL,8,Flessons had been learnt from last
OL,9,Fyear's event, an example given were
OL,10,Fthe drop-off zones in the current
OL,11,Fplans which were absent in 2025.
OL,13,FDespite a lengthy debate between
OL,14,Fcouncillors, the plans were ultimately
OL,15,Fapproved with seven councils voting
OL,16,Fyes, one voting no and one abstaining.
OL,18,FBlackweir Live 2026 will run from June
OL,19,F24 to July 4 and will see The Cure,
OL,20,FLewis Capaldi, Pitbull and Teddy Swims
OL,21,Fperform.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/6
